            <h1 id="parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state-for-food-and-animal-welfare">Parliamentary Under Secretary of State for Food and Animal Welfare</h1>
            <div class="govspeak">
<p>Responsibilities include:</p>

<ul>
  <li>animal welfare</li>
  <li>climate change adaptation</li>
  <li>EU exit readiness oversight</li>
  <li>food chain - with the lead for Food and Drink Industrial Strategy</li>
  <li>forestry</li>
</ul>

</div>
